The article discusses the benefits of the Tax Cuts and Jobs Act signed into law by President Donald J. Trump. It highlights three main points: 

1. Encouraging entrepreneurship: The Tax Cuts and Jobs Act will provide small business owners with the opportunity to grow and thrive.

2. Greater opportunity for workers: The Act is expected to spur business growth and job creation, ultimately benefiting American workers.

3. Revitalizing communities: The Act aims to expand economic opportunity in underserved communities.